node.text: @themarcjacobs I am always excited and honored to get a glimpse into your mind. Walking this show first bundled up and masked , and then walking again with layers and masks removed, was a celebratory & symbolic experience. This whole collection made me feel like I took a walk with Marc down the snowy, empty, streets of the pandemic-height NYC and got to see his imagination come to life and fill the city again. Thank you for having me & to everyone on  @alastairmckimm @diane.kendal @jimmypaulhair @marcjacobs @samuel_ellis teams for everything. Big love!
